&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/AFR-MARRAKECH-LA-TABLE-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-7439&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/AFR-MARRAKECH-LA-TABLE-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;AFR- MARRAKECH- LA TABLE- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;75&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;On the edge of the Medina located within the Royal Mansour, a hotel commissioned by King Mohammed VI only a few years back, La Grande Table Marocaine is one of the most beautiful and tastefully opulent restaurants in the world. Exotic tiles, soft lighting, rich velvets, the glow of filigreed metal tables and a staff in traditional Moroccan dress set the stage for an exquisite dining experience. The restaurant, included in the exclusive Les Grandes Tables du Monde restaurant association, is overseen by Michelin 3 star chef&nbsp;Yannick All&eacute;no&lt;em&gt;,&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;who creates traditional Moroccan cuisine with a contemporary twist.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact La Grande Table Marocaine by phone at&nbsp;+212-529-80-82-82 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:restauration@royalmansour.ma&quot;&gt;restauration@royalmansour.ma&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: As a courtesy, if you need to cancel your reservation please do so within 24 hours of the dining date&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arise.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment must be made with your Diners Club card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

